{
  "stem": "17606.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 147.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- with that-- my stubbornness, I am the Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nothing-- and-- and no one will bother-- nothing will bother me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I gained respect.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But such a respect, not a presentation from my division could go without me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They always included me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I became the beloved Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like this.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to say, every-- every Pole has his [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I become-- may-- maybe I became their [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my commanding officer of school said to me I got of-- out of-- out of 300, I had-- you say-- a round of graduates, they got it-- it's a different position in it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not the same when it's-- when he is listed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was the twelfth listed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my commanding officer said to me, you know, you have a right to be dissatisfied with it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was I couldn't put a Jew higher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I think I was very happy with-- with twelfth location.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I was sent to the city of [POLISH], which is hundred-- close to-- very close to the German border.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a lot of this-- of Volksdeutsche there, living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ethnic German.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but that was before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was 1938.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was there in basic training till three months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I came home a few months later, and I was graduated as a platoon leader-- a platoon leader, actually.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after that, I came home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Started to practice at-- finish?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
